Update the scripts on ebics server (ebics1.rz01.deposit-solutions.com)

  $ ssh ebics1.rz01.deposit-solutions.com

  $ su - idcard

  [idcard@ebics1 persoupload]$ vi upload_single_id_card_or_cor.sh

    - Add the bank details as below
    - Example:

      change-1:

        BREL)
                BANK='libra'
                ;;

      change-2:

                BREL)
                        sftp ${SSHUSER}@${HOST} << EOF
                                cd outbox
                                cd id_card_copies
                                put $FILE
          EOF
                        ;;

    $ exit

    $

    - switch to the "cor" user and make entries on the below files:

      $ su - cor

       - check_for_duplicates.sh
       - distribute.sh
       - pre_check_all.sh
       - collect_all.sh
       - send_cors.sh

